00:30:07,760 --> 00:30:11,160
We are working on a process to promote people,

521
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:14,200
to make it more, to write down things.

522
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:17,200
We are working on a mentoring guide

523
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:19,440
to explain what is mentoring,

524
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:21,600
how to mentor, what does it mean.

